title: 222: 10 Takeaways from Week 7
itunes:title: 222: 10 Takeaways from Week 7
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks give you their ten biggest takeaways following all of Sunday's action. Are the Chargers the best team in the AFC West (7:45)? Is Todd Gurley the NFL's best back(11:45)? Who is the best player nobody is talking about(15:10)? Find out on this episode of Move the Sticks.
